IT Hits. CRIT Rate and CRIT DMG are fixed at 20% and 100% respectively.<br><strong>·</strong> Within 8s of being affected by Quicken, Aggravate, Spread, DEF is decreased by 30%.\",\r\n      \"Pledge of Propriety\" : \"Increases the Level of All Schemes to Know by 3. Maximum upgrade level is 15.\",\r\n      \"Shogun\'s Descent\" : \"When 1/2/3/4 (or more) nearby opponents are affected by All Schemes to Know\'s Seeds of Skandha, Nahida\'s Elemental Mastery will be increased by 100/120/140/160.\",\r\n      \"Shinkage Bygones\" : \"Increases the Level of Illusory Heart by 3. Maximum upgrade level is 15.\",\r\n      \"Wishbearer\" : \"When Nahida hits an opponent affected by All Schemes to Know\'s Seeds of Skandha with Normal or Charged Attacks after unleashing Illusory Heart, she will use Tri-Karma Purification: Karmic Oblivion on this opponent and all connected opponents, dealing Dendro DMG based on 200% of Nahida\'s ATK and 400% of her Elemental Mastery.<br>DMG dealt by Tri-Karma Purification: Karmic Oblivion is considered Elemental Skill DMG and can be triggered once every 0.2s.<br>This effect can last up to 10s and will be removed after Nahida has unleashed 6 instances of Tri-Karma Purification: Karmic Oblivion.\"\r\n    }\r\n  }'),
